<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_108_r1l1">Wir ~ die <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> deʒ Rats <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> Tun kunt offenlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l2">mit <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> brief / Als vns des <expan>hochgebor<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l3"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ludwigs Rete / <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ſie die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l4">klage <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanſen <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Lantricht<ex>er</ex>s</expan> cʒü Hirſperg <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l5"><expan>geſlage<ex>n</ex></expan> haben / bis auf den nehſten ſant Mıchels tag / Alſo / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l6">wir den aufſlag vor <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>nehſte<ex>n</ex></expan> lantgericht <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllen / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l7">Alſo ſchıcken wir <expan>Conrat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Pilſacher vnd <expan>Hanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> Stecʒman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l8">vnſer <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt / das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l9">alſo 
<del rend="strikethrough">vor de </del> cʒehandeln vnd den aufſlag <expan>cʒeneme<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd cʒetün </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_line_1573065554378_202">an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat / . Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> <expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>vvalp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_108" id="53v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> dez rats
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czü
                                                  <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, tun kunt
                                                offenlich mit <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> brief,
                                                als uns des <expan>hochgebor<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ludwigs, rete
                                                  <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie die klage
                                                  <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hansen
                                                  <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                                                  <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex>s</expan> czü Hirsperg,
                                                  <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                          auf<expan>geslage<ex>n</ex></expan> haben bis <app><note><q type="date">auf
                                            den nehsten sant Michels tag</q>29.09.1410</note></app>, also daz wir den
                                                aufslag vor <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>nehste<ex>n</ex></expan> lantgericht
                                                  <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> süllen. Also
                                                schicken wir <expan>Conrat<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                Pilsacher und <expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                Steczman, unser <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, und
                                                  <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den
                                                  <expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt, das also
                                                cze handeln und den aufslag <expan>cze
                                                  neme<ex>n</ex></expan> und cze tün an
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat. Mit
                                                  <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>is</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
